<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，有一个寡妇和她的儿子杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很穷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们住在一个又小又破的房子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，我饿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们今晚能吃点儿东西吗？”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，我们没有食物了。”他的妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天我们把奶牛卖了吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经太老了，没有奶水了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你把它带到市场上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把它卖了后买些面包和肉回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，妈妈。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，在去往市场的路上，杰克遇到了一个矮个子老人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你的奶牛卖给我吧。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把这颗豆给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！这颗豆怎么能让我和妈妈吃饱呢？”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一颗有魔力的豆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它会向天空长出一根高高的藤！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天上有一个充满魔力的王国，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且到处都是美好的东西。”老人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“云上面可能有食物和钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他把奶牛卖给了老人，换取了一颗豆子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克兴奋地跑回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，面包和肉在哪儿？”他的妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看，妈妈。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把奶牛卖了，换了这颗魔法豆！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？你这个笨蛋！这颗豆子能做什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们今晚又要挨饿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把豆子扔到了后院里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，杰克向外面看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，看！院里有一根巨大的豆茎！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！去拿斧头把它砍断。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是杰克相信那个老人的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他顺着豆茎爬到了最顶部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他到达顶部的时候，他不敢相信自己的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>云层里有一个巨大的城堡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克敲了敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个佣人开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊，是一个小男孩儿！你在这里做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想看看云层上面有什么。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘，安静点儿！”佣人警告说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的主人是一个巨人，他专门吃小孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他现在就在楼上。你必须藏起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说一个巨人住在这里？天啊！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！快，快躲进炉子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的主人马上就要下楼了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在佣人把杰克推进炉子里的时候，巨人来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我闻到了一个小男孩儿的味道！”巨人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里没有其他人。是你想象出来的吧！”佣人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，好吧。”巨人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我的鹅拿来！”他吩咐道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想要会唱歌的竖琴吗？”佣人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。我数金蛋的时候让竖琴来点儿音乐。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人坐到了桌子前面，佣人拿来了鹅和竖琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我的鹅，快给我下金蛋吧。哈哈！”巨人大笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克通过炉子上的洞向外看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他看到那只鹅下了金蛋的时候，惊呆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！我还是能闻到一个小孩子的味道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人嘟囔着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”巨人开始到处寻找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在巨人要打开炉子看的时候，佣人把鹅赶走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，主人！鹅飞走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人回头看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？快回来！”他大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快，小男孩儿！快离开这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佣人告诉他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，唱着歌的竖琴喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站住！你是谁？你在这里干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是竖琴不听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“主人，主人！我发现了一个男孩儿！”竖琴喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”巨人咆哮道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚饭把你吃了一定很美味！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克很快逃到罐子之间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人跑来抓杰克，但是杰克太小了，他找不到他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，你在哪儿，小男孩儿？出来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人在寻找杰克的时候，杰克溜了出来，快速逃离了城堡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，主人！看！他逃跑了。”竖琴喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>354408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人追了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>354409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是正当他跑出城门的时候，佣人关上了门，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门夹到了巨人的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人被绊倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>365285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>366789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>366790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当杰克跑到豆茎的时候，他看到了那只鹅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>372562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>375384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那只鹅！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>375385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>381390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克抓住它，迅速地顺着豆茎爬了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>381391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>386518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人跑到豆茎旁，也开始顺着它爬下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>386519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>394210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他的速度没有杰克那么快，于是杰克先到达了地面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>89</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>394211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>399239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，妈妈，快！斧头在哪儿？”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>90</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>399240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>401449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰克，你去哪儿了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>91</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>401450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>404530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你把斧头留在这里了。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>92</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>404531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>409008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克拿起斧头开始向豆茎砍去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>93</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>409009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>412608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是豆茎开始前后摇晃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>94</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>412609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>418772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！豆茎要倒了！”巨人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>95</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>418773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>421763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨人努力地抓住豆茎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>96</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>421764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>428717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是很快他就松手掉了下来，摔死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>97</Number>
